      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<ab>[Success!] Slabs (decorating) the āyāga(-platform) were [erected] by the pupil of the venerable <persName key="pers:Kan-Śāntika">Sa(ṃ)taka</persName> (Śānaika?) of the teachers [from <placeName key="pl:Koruṅkala">Koru(ṃ)gāla</placeName>], the nun <persName key="pers:Kan-Dharmarakṣitā">Dhamarakhitā</persName> (Dharmarakṣitā) [...]</ab>
